- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper deals with controlling the behavior of a large-scale robot swarm. 
- cs.DS (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is a possible category as the paper deals with a decentralized approach for deployment of a robot swarm. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is also a possible category as the paper deals with constructing a logical tree topology over the physical network formed by the robots.
